{
  "text": "A Laguerre-Gauss mode with radial subindex p and azimuthal index \u2113 is given, in cylindrical coordinates r; \u03d5; z, by [CITATION_1] LG \u2113 p A p;\u2113 r j\u2113j e i\u2113\u03d5 GL j\u2113j p W p;\u2113 ;",
